OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,6,Fbright spells and occasional sunny
OL,7,Fintervals along with some showers,
OL,8,Fthese possibly on the heavy side in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,12,Fclear intervals and scattered showers,
OL,13,Fthese more frequent in the evening
OL,14,Fbefore turning isolated overnight as
OL,15,Fwinds fall light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FAnother mixed day with some
OL,18,Fbrighter spells but also some showers,
OL,19,Fthese becoming isolated later in the
OL,20,Fday. Lighter winds but a bit colder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
