OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FSaturday should stay dry with some
OL,7,Fsunshine. Dry much of Sunday then rain
OL,8,Fspreading from northwest in the
OL,9,Fevening. Sunshine and isolated showers
OL,10,Fon Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
